Class FlipFitGym

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitGym
public class FlipFitGym extends Object
The `FlipFitGym` class represents a gym entity within the FlipFit system. It encapsulates all the essential details of a gym, including its unique ID, name, location, and operational information.
